        "content": "<p>Directly calculate using a calculator: sin(20°) ≈ 0.34202.<br>\nCompare: 1/3 ≈ 0.33333, and 7/20 = 0.35000. <br>\nClearly, 0.33333 &lt; 0.34202 &lt; 0.35000.</p>",
